{"title":"我的训练计划","date":"2019-07-28T00:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 28, 2019","L":"07/28/2019","MM-DD":"07-28"},"updated":"2020-03-29T17:55:35.510Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>原载于博客：<a href=\"https://media.weibo.cn/article?id=2309404059594304394906&amp;display=0&amp;retcode=6102\" target=\"_blank\">训练方法分享：什么是”推拉腿”锻炼法，附健身计划</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"锻炼1-推部日\">锻炼1-推部日<a title=\"#锻炼1-推部日\" href=\"#锻炼1-推部日\"></a></h3>\n<p>卧推：3组，每组5-7个<br>\n坐姿哑铃肩推举：3X6-8<br>\n上斜哑铃推举：3X8-10<br>\n侧平举：2X10-12<br>\n三头肌下拉：2X8-10<br>\n颈后三头肌屈臂伸：2X8-10</p>\n<h3 id=\"锻炼2-拉部日\">锻炼2-拉部日<a title=\"#锻炼2-拉部日\" href=\"#锻炼2-拉部日\"></a></h3>\n<p>俯身哑铃（或杠铃）划船：3X5-7<br>\n引体向上：3X6-8<br>\n杠铃耸肩：3X8-10<br>\n绳索面拉：2X10-12<br>\n杠铃弯举：2X8-10<br>\n哑铃锤式弯举：2X8-10</p>\n<h3 id=\"锻炼3-腿（腹）部日\">锻炼3-腿（腹）部日<a title=\"#锻炼3-腿（腹）部日\" href=\"#锻炼3-腿（腹）部日\"></a></h3>\n<p>深蹲：3X6-8<br>\n罗马尼亚硬拉：2X8-10<br>\n腿蹬举：2X10-12<br>\n腿弯举：2X10-12<br>\n小腿上提：4X8-10<br>\n悬垂抬腿：2X10-15</p>\n","link":"others/FitPlan","comments":true,"plink":"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/others/FitPlan/","toc":[{"id":"锻炼1-推部日","title":"锻炼1-推部日","index":"1"},{"id":"锻炼2-拉部日","title":"锻炼2-拉部日","index":"2"},{"id":"锻炼3-腿（腹）部日","title":"锻炼3-腿（腹）部日","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/others/FitPlan/\" title=\"我的训练计划\">https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/others/FitPlan/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"July 28, 2019","updated":"March 29, 2020"}}